description: Giacomo Dalla Torre, the head of the Catholic chivalric group, helped smooth ties with the Vatican.
title: Order of Malta: Grand Master Giacomo Dalla Torre dies at 75
title_page: Order of Malta: Grand Master Giacomo Dalla Torre dies at 75 - BBC News
maintext: It is also known commonly as the Knights of Malta, although its full title is the Sovereign Military Hospitaller Order of St John of Jerusalem, of Rhodes and of Malta.
